<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Cognito Configuration Required</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 100px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #d73027;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .message {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffc107;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    code {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-family: monospace;
    }
    .steps {
      background-color: #e7f3ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #0066cc;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .steps ol {
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Cognito Configuration Required</h1>
  
  <div class="message">
    <p><strong>Cognito credentials are not configured yet.</strong></p>
    <p>Please add the <code>cognito:</code> key to your Rails credentials file to enable authentication.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="steps">
    <h2>Configuration Steps:</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Run Terraform to create Cognito resources (if not done yet):
        <pre><code>cd terraform/environments/dev
terraform init
terraform apply</code></pre>
      </li>
      <li>Get Terraform outputs for Cognito configuration:
        <pre><code>terraform output -json</code></pre>
      </li>
      <li>Edit Rails credentials for development:
        <pre><code>bin/rails credentials:edit --environment development</code></pre>
      </li>
      <li>Add Cognito configuration in the credentials file:
        <pre><code>cognito:
  domain: balansi-dev-xxxxx  # From terraform output (cognito_domain)
  region: sa-east-1  # From terraform output (cognito_region)
  client_id: xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx  # From terraform output (cognito_client_id)
  client_secret: xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx  # From terraform output (cognito_client_secret)
  redirect_uri: http://localhost:3000/auth/callback
  logout_uri: http://localhost:3000</code></pre>
      </li>
      <li>Save and close the editor - Rails will encrypt the file automatically</li>
      <li>Restart the Rails server for changes to take effect</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <p><a href="/">‚Üê Back to Home</a></p>
</body>
</html>